<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>杂谈 on 编程心语</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/tags/%E6%9D%82%E8%B0%88/</link><description>Recent content in 杂谈 on 编程心语</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 18 Jul 2018 18:34:58 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.ithome.me/tags/%E6%9D%82%E8%B0%88/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Udacity也弃用React Native了 ！</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2018/07/18/udacity%E4%B9%9F%E5%BC%83%E7%94%A8react-native%E4%BA%86-/</link><pubDate>Wed, 18 Jul 2018 18:34:58 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2018/07/18/udacity%E4%B9%9F%E5%BC%83%E7%94%A8react-native%E4%BA%86-/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;不久之前，Airbnb 团队刚刚宣布放弃使用React Native，才过不久，Udacity移动团队最近也宣布从App中移除了使用React Native开发的最后一批功能。再加上6月中旬，Facebook宣布将大规模重构RN，这一系列的事件，让不少正在使用React Native的开发者瑟瑟发抖，陷入了恐慌之中。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>